                Users would have the ability to like, comment, and share.

    %section 
        %h2.s4 Idea 2: A mentoring forum
        %p Another product idea that we explored was a discussion group for alumni focused on sharing expertise and advice on professional issues. We built a static prototype for 1-on-1 user testing. We also created a Google Group discussion to test actual user interactions.
